  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Colorado 1-Quad Zoom VWis a bright indoor/outdoor PAR-style variable white wash light featuring seven 15 W Osram quad-LEDs with tunable color temperature, from 2800 K to 9010 K, to match tungsten sources up to and beyond daylight. A zoom range of 15 to 49 deg, and five dimming curves allow the creative use of the fixture as a beam, wide flood, and wash. It maintains its IP65 rating with IP rated DMX cables, but standard 5-pin XLR DMX cables work perfectly for indoor use.",
